---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/styles.css';

// Define the weeks data directly for now
const weeks = [
    { number: 0, title: "S3tup & 0nb04rd1ng", subtitle: "Environment Configuration - Dev tools mastery", status: "available" },
    { number: 1, title: "Th3 F1r5t T4g", subtitle: "Single Tag Mastery - Understanding HTML anatomy", status: "locked"},
    { number: 2, title: "D0cum3nt 4rch1t3ctur3", subtitle: "Structure Before Style - Valid HTML foundations", status: "locked" },
    { number: 3, title: "Th3 C4sc4d3 B3g1n5", subtitle: "CSS Separation of Concerns", status: "locked" },
    { number: 4, title: "F0rm5 & 1nput5", subtitle: "User Interaction Patterns", status: "locked" },
    { number: 5, title: "Fl3xb0x M45t3ry", subtitle: "One-dimensional Layouts", status: "locked" },
    { number: 6, title: "Tr1but3 P4g3", subtitle: "First Complete Project", status: "locked" },
    { number: 7, title: "Gr1d Sy5t3m5", subtitle: "Two-dimensional Thinking", status: "locked" },
    { number: 8, title: "Pr0duct L4nd1ng", subtitle: "Professional Product Page", status: "locked" },
    { number: 9, title: "P0rtf0l10 Sy5t3m", subtitle: "Personal Brand Development (2 weeks)", status: "locked" },
    { number: 11, title: "Sh1p 1t", subtitle: "Launch & Deploy", status: "locked" }
];
---

<BaseLayout title="Home - DESN368">
    <!-- Breadcrumb Navigation -->
    <nav class="breadcrumb-nav">
        <div class="breadcrumb-container">
            <div class="breadcrumb">
                <span class="breadcrumb-current">Course Overview</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="course-content two-column">
        <div class="main-content fade-in">
            <!-- Course Introduction -->
            <section class="card card-accent accent-block card-enhanced">
                <div class="color-bar color-bar-red"></div>
                <h2>
                    <span class="icon-enhanced icon-primary">
                        <svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16">
                            <path d="M5.433 2.304A4.492 4.492 0 0 0 3.5 6c0 1.598.832 3.002 2.09 3.802.518.329 1.169.548 1.91.548.741 0 1.392-.219 1.91-.548C10.668 9.002 11.5 7.598 11.5 6a4.492 4.492 0 0 0-1.933-3.696A.25.25 0 0 0 9.25 2.5H6.75a.25.25 0 0 0-.317-.196ZM6 12.5h4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1H6a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    Welcome to the <span class="text-gradient">Real Thing</span>
                </h2>
                <p>Most people live on the <strong>surface</strong> of the webâ€”scrolling, clicking, tapping. But beneath all of that, there's <span style="color: var(--brand-primary); font-weight: 600;">structure</span>. <span style="color: var(--brand-red); font-weight: 600;">Logic</span>. <strong>Craft</strong>.</p>

                <p>In this class, you'll learn to read and write the <code>source code</code> that powers the modern internet. Not with drag-and-drop tools. Not through shortcuts. But with the foundational toolsâ€”<span style="background: rgba(212, 24, 61, 0.1); color: var(--brand-red); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: var(--font-mono);">HTML</span> and <span style="background: rgba(3, 2, 19, 0.1); color: var(--brand-primary); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: var(--font-mono);">CSS</span>â€”the way it actually works.</p>

                <p>You'll start from <strong>nothing</strong>. Build from <strong>scratch</strong>. And by the end, you won't just have a few websites. You'll have a <span style="color: var(--brand-primary); font-weight: 600;">lens</span>â€”a way of seeing and shaping digital space that most people never access.</p>

                <div style="padding: 20px; background: var(--gradient-accent); border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--brand-red); margin: 20px 0;">
                    <p style="font-style: italic; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0;">
                        ðŸ’» This isn't a bootcamp. This isn't a YouTube tutorial. <span style="color: var(--brand-red); font-weight: 700;">This is the real thing.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="section-divider with-icon"></div>

            <!-- Student Pledge -->
            <section class="card accent-block-subtle card-enhanced">
                <h2>
                    <span class="icon-enhanced">
                        <svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16">
                            <path d="M9.504.43a1.516 1.516 0 0 1 2.437 1.713L10.415 5.5h2.123c1.57 0 2.346 1.909 1.22 3.004l-7.34 7.142a1.249 1.249 0 0 1-.871.354h-.302a1.25 1.25 0 0 1-1.157-1.723L5.633 10.5H3.462c-1.57 0-2.346-1.909-1.22-3.004L9.503.429Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    Student Pledge
                    <span class="badge badge-primary">Required</span>
                </h2>
                <div class="code-block">
                    $ "I will not blindly copy and paste.<br>
                    I will write my own tags.<br>
                    I will read the source.<br>
                    I will not fear the browser inspector.<br>
                    I will know what my code does.<br>
                    I will build with intent."
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Course Structure -->
            <section class="card card-enhanced">
                <div class="color-bar color-bar-multi"></div>
                <h2>
                    <span class="icon-enhanced">
                        <svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16">
                            <path d="M0 1.75A.75.75 0 0 1 .75 1h4.253c1.227 0 2.317.59 3 1.501A3.743 3.743 0 0 1 11.006 1h4.245a.75.75 0 0 1 .75.75v10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-.75.75h-4.507a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-1.591.659l-.622.621a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0l-.622-.621A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.258 13H.75a.75.75 0 0 1-.75-.75V1.75Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    Course Structure: 11 Weeks of Foundation
                </h2>
                <div class="week-list">
                    {weeks.map((week) => (
                        <div class="week-item">
                            <div>
                                <h3>
                                    <span class={`status-dot status-${week.status}`}></span>
                                    {week.status === "available" ? (
                                        <a href={`/weeks/week-${week.number}`}>
                                            Week {week.number}: {week.title}
                                        </a>
                                    ) : (
                                        `Week ${week.number}: ${week.title}`
                                    )}
                                </h3>
                                <p>{week.subtitle}</p>
                            </div>
                            <span class={`state-label state-label-${week.status}`}>
                                {week.status === "available" ? "Available" : "Coming Soon"}
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <!-- Brick by Brick Method -->
            <section class="card accent-block card-enhanced">
                <h2>
                    <span class="icon-enhanced">
                        <svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16">
                            <path d="M7.122.392a1.75 1.75 0 0 1 1.756 0l5.003 2.902c.83.481.83 1.68 0 2.162L8.878 8.358a1.75 1.75 0 0 1-1.756 0L2.119 5.456a1.25 1.25 0 0 1 0-2.162L7.122.392ZM8.125 1.69a.25.25 0 0 0-.25 0l-4.63 2.685 4.63 2.685a.25.25 0 0 0 .25 0l4.63-2.685L8.125 1.69ZM1.601 7.789a.75.75 0 0 1 1.025-.273L8 10.424l5.374-2.908a.75.75 0 1 1 .752 1.298L8.752 11.85a.75.75 0 0 1-.752 0l-5.374-2.908a.75.75 0 0 1-.273-1.025Zm0 3.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.025-.273L8 13.924l5.374-2.908a.75.75 0 1 1 .752 1.298L8.752 15.35a.75.75 0 0 1-.752 0l-5.374-2.908a.75.75 0 0 1-.273-1.025Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    The "Brick by Brick" Method
                </h2>
                
                <h3>Micro-Skills Architecture</h3>
                <p>Each assignment builds one tiny, specific skill that becomes the foundation for the next. You cannot proceed to Assignment B until you demonstrate mastery of Assignment A through multiple assessment gates.</p>
                
                <h3>Four Types of Mastery Gates</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Technical Gate</strong> - Code validates and works perfectly</li>
                    <li><strong>Conceptual Gate</strong> - Can explain why it works</li>
                    <li><strong>Debug Gate</strong> - Can fix broken code</li>
                    <li><strong>Teaching Gate</strong> - Can help a classmate understand</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>No Student Left Behind</h3>
                <p>Multiple learning pathways accommodate different learning styles:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Visual learners:</strong> Figma integration and visual diagrams</li>
                    <li><strong>Kinesthetic learners:</strong> Hands-on coding from day one</li>
                    <li><strong>Analytical learners:</strong> Deep documentation and technical specs</li>
                    <li><strong>Social learners:</strong> Peer teaching and pair programming</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Why This Works</h3>
                <p>Traditional courses throw everything at you at once. You memorize, you forget. This course builds muscle memory. Each micro-skill becomes automatic before you move on. By Week 11, you won't have to think about syntaxâ€”your fingers will know.</p>
            </section>
        </div>

        <aside class="sidebar">
            <!-- Quick Actions -->
            <section class="card card-action card-enhanced">
                <div class="color-bar color-bar-red"></div>
                <h3>
                    <span class="icon-enhanced icon-primary">
                        <svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16">
                            <path d="M9.504.43a1.516 1.516 0 0 1 2.437 1.713L10.415 5.5h2.123c1.57 0 2.346 1.909 1.22 3.004l-7.34 7.142a1.249 1.249 0 0 1-.871.354h-.302a1.25 1.25 0 0 1-1.157-1.723L5.633 10.5H3.462c-1.57 0-2.346-1.909-1.22-3.004L9.503.429Z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    Quick Actions
                    <span class="badge badge-warning">New</span>
                </h3>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
                    <a href="/syllabus" class="btn btn-secondary">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="margin-right: 6px;">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
                        </svg>
                        View Syllabus
                    </a>
                    <a href="/weeks/week-0" class="btn btn-start">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" style="margin-right: 6px;">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM9.555 7.168A1 1 0 008 8v4a1 1 0 001.555.832l3-2a1 1 0 000-1.664l-3-2z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        Start Week 0
                    </a>
                    
                    <a href="https://github.com/sicxz/desn368-f25" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">
                        <svg width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" style="margin-right: 6px;">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 0C4.477 0 0 4.484 0 10.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0110 4.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.203 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.942.359.31.678.921.678 1.856 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0020 10.017C20 4.484 15.522 0 10 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>
                        GitHub Repo
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Course Tools -->
            <section class="card">
                <h3>
                    <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="margin-right: 6px;">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z"/>
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Essential Tools
                </h3>

                <!-- VS Code Block -->
                <div class="tool-block">
                    <h4>VS Code</h4>
                    <p>Your code editor for the semester</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Download VS Code</a>
                </div>

                <!-- CodePen Block -->
                <div class="tool-block">
                    <h4>CodePen</h4>
                    <p>Online playground for quick experiments</p>
                    <a href="https://codepen.io/" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">Create Account</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Chrome DevTools Block -->
                <div class="tool-block">
                    <h4>Chrome DevTools</h4>
                    <p>Browser inspector and debugging tools</p>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn DevTools</a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Philosophy Quote -->
            <section class="card card-accent" style="position: relative;">
                <div style="position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 16px; opacity: 0.1; transform: rotate(12deg);">
                    <i data-lucide="quote" style="width: 48px; height: 48px; color: var(--brand-primary);"></i>
                </div>
                <blockquote style="font-style: italic; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.6; position: relative; z-index: 1; margin: 0;">
                    <span style="font-size: 20px;">"</span>We're not making pretty pages. We're building <span style="color: var(--brand-primary); font-weight: 700;">digital infrastructure</span>.<span style="font-size: 20px;">"</span>
                </blockquote>
                <div style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted);">â€” Course Philosophy</div>
            </section>

            <!-- Quick Reference -->
            <section class="card">
                <h3>
                    <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" style="margin-right: 6px;">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
                    </svg>
                    Quick Reference
                </h3>

                <!-- HTML Tags -->
                <div class="reference-section">
                    <button class="reference-toggle" onclick="toggleReference('html')">
                        <span>HTML Tags</span>
                        <svg class="chevron" id="html-chevron" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="reference-content" id="html-content">
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">&lt;h1&gt;</span>
                            <span class="desc">Main heading</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">&lt;p&gt;</span>
                            <span class="desc">Paragraph</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">&lt;a&gt;</span>
                            <span class="desc">Link</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">&lt;img&gt;</span>
                            <span class="desc">Image</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">&lt;div&gt;</span>
                            <span class="desc">Container</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- CSS Properties -->
                <div class="reference-section">
                    <button class="reference-toggle" onclick="toggleReference('css')">
                        <span>CSS Properties</span>
                        <svg class="chevron" id="css-chevron" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                        </svg>
                    </button>
                    <div class="reference-content" id="css-content">
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">color</span>
                            <span class="desc">Text color</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">background</span>
                            <span class="desc">Background color</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">font-size</span>
                            <span class="desc">Text size</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="reference-item">
                            <span class="tag">margin</span>
